Let's install ZK grails plugin which contains all the ZK components and the zk framework. Run the following command inside the emsapp directory.
{code}
grails install-plugin zk 1.0.6
{code}
By installing this plugin, 5 more new grails commands gets installed.
* grails create-comet
* grails create-composer
* grails create-facade
* grails create-zul
* grails install-zk-xml

